            "summary": "This chapter does not apply to Gibraltar-based firms exercising entitlements under the Financial Services and Markets Act 2000 (Gibraltar) Order 2001.",
            "as_at_date": "31/12/2020"
          },
          {
            "rule_number": "4.2",
            "summary": "Unless otherwise indicated in 4, the due date for payment of regulatory transaction fees is on or before the application is made.",
            "as_at_date": "01/03/2016"
